name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: ipc.[port_number].scheduler.priority.levels
description:
How many priority levels to use within the scheduler and call
    queue. This property applies to RpcScheduler and CallQueue.

name: dfs.namenode.top.window.num.buckets
description: Number of buckets in the rolling window implementation of nntop

name: dfs.ls.limit
description:
Limit the number of files printed by ls. If less or equal to
    zero, at most DFS_LIST_LIMIT_DEFAULT (= 1000) will be printed.

name: ftp.bytes-per-checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  ftp.stream-buffer-size
